subject: Audio recordings of the letters?
msgSnippet: I am new to this and am having a hard time distinguishing between some of the vowels. I suspect my difficulty lies with the fact that I do not pronounce words
messageBody: I am new to this and am having a hard time distinguishing between some of the vowels. I suspect my difficulty lies with the fact that I do not pronounce words the same as Read. (I'm Canadian) Has anyone created a recording of the various letters being spoken, along with their examples?
